{"tid":2415134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美跨黨派議員提譴責決議案，譴責北京在港侵犯權利自由","createTime":"2021-02-20T04:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T04:17:44.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90c65fab8719862f95680a9105fae3af28acb1b2","tid":2415134,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424684&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbknljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=b121ec15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424684&h=40c12767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424684</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有美國民主共和兩黨眾議員提出決議案，譴責北京在本港侵犯權利及自由。<br />\n<br />\n決議案指，中國政府實施港區國安法，可能違反《基本法》，並批評特區政府相繼撤銷民主派人士參選資格，並在今年初逮捕多名泛民人士。<br />\n<br />\n決議案重申眾議院支持港人，並鼓勵美國政府與盟友合作，對港人提供保護及呼籲政府部門持續對相關涉入中港官員實施制裁，及要求美國公司注意港區國安法對美國安全及公民的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院外交事務委員會下周將審議決議案，相信會獲通過。但決議案只表達國會立場，對政府並無約束力。"},{"pid":"b391717ac775a7ae975816ae6474f28ebda7b85f","tid":2415134,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UykmbHa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUykmbHa.gif&h=cc3c2042&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}